\id PHP - Plain English Version 
\h Philippians 
\toc3 Philippians 
\toc2 Philippians 
\toc1 Paul’s Letter to the Philippians 
\mt1 The letter that Paul wrote to the Christians at Philippi  
\mt2 (The book in the Holy Bible called \bk Philippians\bk*)  
\imt1 About this letter  
\ip Paul wrote this letter about 2,000 years ago, about 30 years after Jesus went back to heaven, and it is now in the Holy Bible.  
\ip God sent Paul to lots of towns to tell people about Jesus, and one of them was Philippi (see Acts 16:11-40). It was in the country that we now call Greece, but at that time they called it Macedonia. About 1,400 years ago an earthquake broke Philippi down, and today there are just stones and rubbish at that place in Greece.  
\ip At the time when Paul wrote this letter, the people called the Romans were the bosses over lots of nations. The Roman bosses didn’t like Paul telling people about Jesus, so they grabbed him and put him in jail. Paul wrote this letter while he was in that jail, in Rome. His friend Timothy helped him write it.  
\ip In this letter, Paul said some very important things to help those Christians get really close to God. And we can learn a lot today from what Paul wrote to the Christians at Philippi, a long time ago.  
\cl Chapter  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w am|strong="G1510"\w* \w Paul|strong="G3972"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w* letter \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w from|strong="G2532"\w* me, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w from|strong="G2532"\w* \w Timothy|strong="G5095"\w* \w too|strong="G2532"\w*, \w because|strong="G1722"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w helping|strong="G2532"\w* me write \w it|strong="G2532"\w*. \w We|strong="G2532"\w* \w work|strong="G3956"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w time|strong="G1722"\w* \w for|strong="G1722"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*. \w We|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* sending \w this|strong="G3588"\w* letter \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w God|strong="G2532"\w*’s special \w people|strong="G3956"\w* \w at|strong="G1722"\w* \w Philippi|strong="G5375"\w*, \w you|strong="G1722"\w* \w people|strong="G3956"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w belong|strong="G1510"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*. \w We|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* writing \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G1722"\w* Christian leaders, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G1722"\w* church helpers, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w you|strong="G1722"\w* \w Christians|strong="G2424"\w*.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt Acts 16:12\x*   
\p
