\v 29-30 Epafroditus belongs to our leader, Jesus, just like you do. You couldn’t come and help me a while ago, so he came instead of you. And then he nearly died. But he didn’t worry. He knew he was working for Jesus Christ while he was helping me, and he was ready to die for Jesus. You have to really respect people like Epafroditus. So when he comes back to you, be happy and say, “Good to see you again. You are our good Christian friend.”   
\c 3  
\s1 Some people teach things that are not true  
\p
\v 1 \w And|strong="G1161"\w* \w now|strong="G1161"\w*, \w my|strong="G1722"\w* Christian friends, \w before|strong="G1722"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* finish \w this|strong="G3588"\w* \w letter|strong="G1125"\w*, \w I|strong="G1473"\w* want \w to|strong="G1722"\w* tell \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w*. \w Be|strong="G3756"\w* happy \w all|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w time|strong="G1722"\w*. Remember \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* belong \w to|strong="G1722"\w* \w our|strong="G2962"\w* leader \w Jesus|strong="G2962"\w*. \w Yes|strong="G1161"\w*, \w I|strong="G1473"\w* told \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w all|strong="G1722"\w* \w these|strong="G3588"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w* \w before|strong="G1722"\w*, \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w am|strong="G1473"\w* telling \w you|strong="G5210"\w* again. \w I|strong="G1473"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* get tired \w of|strong="G2962"\w* telling \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w* message \w will|strong="G2962"\w* stop \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w from|strong="G3588"\w* going \w the|strong="G1722"\w* wrong \w way|strong="G1722"\w*.   
\p
\v 2-3 Look out. There are some men that want to teach you the wrong things and get you to go the wrong way. They are like dogs. They go the wrong way. They only want to cut men’s bodies. They say that you don’t belong to God unless you do what the Jewish law says and have a young man operation. They are wrong. We have God’s spirit in us, and he helps us respect God the right way. We know what Jesus Christ did for us, and we trust him. We know that ceremonies that people do will not save us, so we don’t trust them. So really, we are the ones that belong to God. Those people that only follow that Jewish law don’t belong to him.   
